Mistletoe - 2 branches
Harvested with a golden sickle, this sacred mistletoe forms the magical base of the potion.

Roots - 3 assorted roots (mandrake, burdock, and ginseng)
Gathered from the deep forests of Gaul, these roots enhance the potion’s effectiveness in promoting rapid hair growth.

Wild Herbs - A handful
Collected from the meadows, these herbs add vitality and stimulate the scalp.

Field Flowers - A bouquet
These vibrant flowers not only add a pleasant aroma but also nourish and strengthen hair.

Pinch of Salt
Salt from the Atlantic marshes helps to purify the mixture and balance the flavors.

Pinch of Pepper
Freshly ground pepper stimulates circulation, ensuring the potion’s effects reach every hair follicle.
